{"tid":1824574,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咩係港共春袋？","createTime":"2020-01-14T14:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T15:10:42.000Z","uid":137109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51e0cd7d6b9323f19a548d87a3ebaffd73f711d0","tid":1824574,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"1. 首要係政治體制<br />\n政治問題 --&gt; 港共派錢想解決、推老懵董出嚟話當年民生做得唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對策：多啲宣揚點解依家制度嘅不足，你想建立嘅嘢 (eg. 民主選舉、透明議會、洗錢落啱嘅地方、公共資源港人優先)... 基本上呢啲連藍絲都駁唔倒，都會反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 次要係經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色經濟圈 --&gt; 不斷受抹黑、指派黑社會搞黃店<br />\n對策：抗爭融入生活，咪貪懶嫌遠。勿拉高黃店門檻，深黃、小店盡量幫襯多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 狗暴問題<br />\n對策：721, 811, 831, 101, 1118 基本上係佢哋死穴。阻止佢哋用時間沖淡到一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆可轉為連儂資訊，煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS 整文宣教學，呢位youtuber好有心，比個like，支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「 和你設計」(1)活動海報設計教學 Photoshop (粵語) SaiHoHk [ 中文字幕 ]：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RJkvZlMlvKw&amp;list=WL&amp;index=3&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRJkvZlMlvKw%26list%3DWL%26index%3D3%26t%3D0s&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c0be3a71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RJkvZlMlvKw&amp;list=WL&amp;index=3&amp;t=0s</a>"},{"pid":"773bf923c118f6b068d64efd26b3658e02c24e90","tid":1824574,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse